imdb.plot outline: Dr. Mike,Changing Your Reality, the groundbreaking, on location, reality talk show giving viewers the tools and strategies they need to live the life they have always wanted. We cover a broad range of topics, including relationships, stress management, parenting, weight loss, and finding purpose in your life. But no matter what the topic, we always strive to give people practical information that will help them make real and lasting changes.
